description: Looking for a trash bin basket that’s as beautiful as it is functional? Look no further than this gorgeous design-centric wicker garbage can basket. It makes the perfect design addition to your room, not to mention a great way to keep you trash out of sight. It’s also a beautiful shower or housewarming gift. Just fill it with blankets, pillows or another full-sized gift to absolutely make someone else’s day!

This beautiful waste and recycling basket adds a unique design flair to your kitchen decor, your entryway or craft room, too. Made of a large diameter prime-grade kubu rattan woven over a furniture-quality rattan pole, you’re guaranteed to get both strength and durability—not to mention maximum trash storage capacity. Perfect for pet food, recycling or general storage, too.
